headline: Celebrate National Ladder Safety Month by Following Important Safety Practices
summary: Spring is the perfect time to tackle home improvement and maintenance projects such as painting or cleaning gutters. Before you start, take some time to brush up on ladder safety tips – especially when power lines and other electrical equipment are nearby.
